        <headline>Severe Thunderstorm Warning issued July 1 at 4:02PM MDT until July 1 at 4:15PM MDT by NWS Great Falls MT</headline>
        <description>At 402 PM MDT, a severe thunderstorm was located 20 miles north of
Henrys Lake, moving northeast at 20 mph.

HAZARD...60 mph wind gusts.

SOURCE...Radar indicated.

IMPACT...Expect damage to roofs, siding, and trees.

This severe thunderstorm will remain over mainly rural areas of
southeastern Madison County.
</description>
        <instruction>For your protection move to an interior room on the lowest floor of a
building.</instruction>
